This paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories, as it deals with neural architecture search and training of neural networks. It may also be relevant to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks and learning (cs.NE), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) sub-categories, as these areas are closely related to the topic of weight sharing and training of neural networks.
